<div class="page column-box">
	<div class="column">
		<div class="column-side">
			<div class="side-fixed">
				<ul class="o-scroll-list">
					<li><a href="#sec01">首次就诊<br>指南</a></li>
					<li><a href="#sec02">就诊流程</a></li>
					<li><a href="#sec04">预约指南</a></li>
					<li><a href="#sec05">知情同意</a></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="column-main">
			<section id="sec01" class="guide-cont-box">
				<header class="page-main-head guide-title-head">
					<h3>首次就诊指南</h3>
				</header>
				<div class="guide-cont">
					<p>首次就诊请务必携带医保卡。<br>如有以下材料，也请一并携带：</p>
					<ul class="dot-green-list first-guide-list">
						<li><span>各类医疗补助证明</span></li>
						<li><span>其他医院的转诊信</span></li>
						<li><span>用药手册</span></li>
						<li><span>其他医院开具的眼药水、口服药</span></li>
						<li><span>学校体检或健康检查结果</span></li>
						
					</ul>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section id="sec02" class="guide-cont-box">
				<header class="page-main-head guide-title-head">
					<h3>就诊流程</h3>
				</header>
				<div class="guide-cont">
					<ul class="medical-flow">
						<li>
							<div class="w-step text-green">STEP<span>01</span></div>
							<div class="medical-flow-text">
								<h4 class="text-green">填写问诊表</h4>
								<p>在前台领取问诊表。<br>请在了解范围内填写症状、正在治疗的疾病、手术史等信息。</p>
							</div>
							<img loading="lazy" src="../wp-content/themes/ikuwaganka/images/step01.svg" alt="STEP01">
						</li>
						<li>
							<div class="w-step text-green">STEP<span>02</span></div>
							<div class="medical-flow-text">
								<h4 class="text-green">问诊检查</h4>
								<p>根据症状进行视力、眼压等必要检查。</p>
							</div>
							<img loading="lazy" src="../wp-content/themes/ikuwaganka/images/step02.svg" alt="STEP02">
						</li>
						<li>
							<div class="w-step text-green">STEP<span>03</span></div>
							<div class="medical-flow-text">
								<h4 class="text-green">诊察</h4>
								<p>医生会对诊察和检查结果进行说明。诊察后可能需要进行更详细的检查或预约。</p>
							</div>
							<img loading="lazy" src="../wp-content/themes/ikuwaganka/images/step03.svg" alt="STEP03">
						</li>
						<li>
							<div class="w-step text-green">STEP<span>04</span></div>
							<div class="medical-flow-text">
								<h4 class="text-green">结算</h4>
								<p>诊察后在前台结算。<br>可以使用现金和信用卡支付。</p>
								<span class="warning">※ 门诊医保可参与大病统筹和家庭共济，丙类检查无法使用职工医保余额。</span>
							</div>
							<img loading="lazy" src="../wp-content/themes/ikuwaganka/images/step04.svg" alt="STEP04">
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="medical-warning">
					<p>如有以下症状，可能需要进行散瞳检查。<br>
						检查后4-5小时会感觉眼睛发亮、视物不清，请勿驾驶汽车、摩托车等交通工具来院。</p>
					<ul class="dot-green-list">
						<li><span>眼部受伤</span></li>
						<li><span>飞蚊症（看到阴影、点状或丝状物）</span></li>
						<li><span>视力突然下降</span></li>
						<li><span>视野缺损（视野部分突然看不见或变得模糊）</span></li>
					</ul>
					<ul class="medocal-warnig-list">
						<li>※ 本院引进了Optos广角眼底相机。即使不散瞳也可以拍摄眼底照片，如果不方便进行散瞳检查，请告知检查人员。</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section id="sec04" class="guide-cont-box">
				<header class="page-main-head guide-title-head">
					<h3>预约指南</h3>
				</header>
				<div class="guide-cont">
					<h4>工作室为了方便患者可接受初诊和复诊预约。<br>专科门诊和特殊检查无需预约即可检查。</h4>
					<p>首次就诊患者可直接预约专家门诊。无需先普通门诊就诊，如有突发症状，请先来院急诊就诊。</p>
					<a class="btn main-btn guide-btn" href="../cataract/index.html">专家门诊指南<span class="arrow">&rarr;</span></a>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section id="sec05" class="guide-cont-box">
				<header class="page-main-head guide-title-head">
					<h3>知情同意</h3>
				</header>
				<div class="guide-cont">
					<p>知情同意是指患者在接受诊疗时，医生对疾病相关的必要检查和治疗进行充分说明，患者在理解并认可的基础上接受治疗的过程。</p>
					<p>工作室会及时向患者说明检查、病情和治疗方法等情况。如果您对说明内容不太理解、想和家人一起再听一遍、想了解不接受检查或治疗会有什么后果等，请告知主治医生或护士。</p>
					<img loading="lazy" src="../wp-content/themes/ikuwaganka/images/ic.jpg" alt="本院会及时向患者说明检查、病情和治疗方法等情况。">
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
